        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/39/2",
        "text": [
          " خَبَرٍ آخَرَ : \"لِلزَّرْعِ إِلَى اَلشِّرَاكَيْنِ وَ لِلنَّخْلِ إِلَى اَلسَّاقَيْنِ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3411 - In another narration: \"For crops, the water should reach up to the two sandal straps, and for palm trees, up to the two shins.\""
          ]
        }
      }
